        "content": "<p>See <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=CategoryTheory.ComposableArrows#doc\">docs#CategoryTheory.ComposableArrows</a>, in particular <code>mk₁</code>.</p>",
